\par }\pard \qj \li0\ri0\sl240\slmult0\nowidctlpar\tx432\tx720\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\b\f1\cf1\insrsid5920122 ACTOR:}{\f1\cf1\insrsid5920122  Ricardo Hoyos Duque.
